>> +Â Â Â  /*
>> +Â Â Â Â  * At this point the expected allocation map is:
>> +Â Â Â Â  *
>> +Â Â Â Â  * 0..c38 - the initial firmware
>> +Â Â Â Â  * 8000..10000 - stack
>> +Â Â Â Â  * 400000.. - kernel
>> +Â Â Â Â  * 3ea0000.. - initramdisk
>> +Â Â Â Â  *
>> +Â Â Â Â  * We skip writing FDT as nothing expects it; OF client interface is
>> +Â Â Â Â  * going to be used for reading the device tree.
